name: MoistCactusAus Adventures
description:
You are in control of a MoistCactusAUS man and your main objective is to get rid off annoying dry cactuses that are trying to attack you!

Be sure to post your high-score down in the comments!

Controls

Movement - WASD

Shooting/Buttons - Mouse 1

Credits

Made for tv./MoistCactusAUS - check out the twitch channel for good vibes & fun!

Made by yt.com/DolphinDev - check out the YouTube channel for more indie game development content!
